                Laborum, reiciendis natus? Quis unde labore commodi mollitia minima debitis.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class=" d-flex flex-md-row-reverse row p-3 my-4">

        <div class="col-md-6 text-center ps-md-5">
            <img src="{{ asset('Pictures/mecanicien_vidange.jpg') }}" alt="vidange de l'huile moteur">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 px-5">
            <p class="text-center text-light w-100 h-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mt-3">
